msgid "Scope: ``scrapy.spidermiddlewares.depth.DepthMiddleware``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/settings.rst:323
msgid ""
"The maximum depth that will be allowed to crawl for any site. If zero, no "
"limit will be imposed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/settings.rst:329
msgid "DEPTH_PRIORITY"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/settings.rst:335
msgid ""
"An integer that is used to adjust the :attr:`~scrapy.http.Request.priority` "
"of a :class:`~scrapy.http.Request` based on its depth."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/settings.rst:338
msgid "The priority of a request is adjusted as follows::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/settings.rst:340
msgid "request.priority = request.priority - ( depth * DEPTH_PRIORITY )"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/settings.rst:342
msgid ""
"As depth increases, positive values of ``DEPTH_PRIORITY`` decrease request "
"priority (BFO), while negative values increase request priority (DFO). See "
"also :ref:`faq-bfo-dfo`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/settings.rst:348
msgid ""
"This setting adjusts priority **in the opposite way** compared to other "
"priority settings :setting:`REDIRECT_PRIORITY_ADJUST` and :setting:"
"`RETRY_PRIORITY_ADJUST`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/settings.rst:355
msgid "DEPTH_STATS_VERBOSE"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/settings.rst:357 ../../../topics/settings.rst:497
#: ../../../topics/settings.rst:730 ../../../topics/settings.rst:934
#: ../../../topics/settings.rst:945 ../../../topics/settings.rst:965
#: ../../../topics/settings.rst:1040 ../../../topics/settings.rst:1142
#: ../../../topics/settings.rst:1191 ../../../topics/settings.rst:1290
msgid "Default: ``False``"
msgstr "預設值：``False``"

#: ../../../topics/settings.rst:361
msgid ""
"Whether to collect verbose depth stats. If this is enabled, the number of "
"requests for each depth is collected in the stats."
